            <div class="col m10 l4 s12 offset-m1 offset-l1">
                <h3 class="event-txt" style="font-size:25px; text-transform: uppercase; font-weight:bold;">Bitcoin And Its Underlying Technology Blockchain</h2>
                <hr>
                <h5 style="font-size: 20px"><img src="img/venue.svg" style="max-width:22px;">  VENUE : iPlex, Vadodara</h5>
                <h5 style="font-size: 20px"><img src="img/calender.svg" style="max-width:22px;">  TIME : March 3rd and 4th 5-7 pm</h5>
                <hr>
                <p class="event-txt">
                    The market cap of cryptocurrencies like Bitcoin and Ethereum was 150 Billion USD in 2017 and hit 800 Billion USD in January 2018, before stabilizing around 500 billion dollars. This event is about discussing the underlying technology behind these cryptocurrencies, Blockchain and its uses, value and future.</p>
                <p class="event-txt"> With the industry developing at a rapid pace, Blockchain Technology is starting to capture the attention of the financial and banking spheres. It has started to spread its roots in medicine, insurance, document circulation, solar, amongst many other industries.
                    The speakers are the people who have the industry experience of trading in cryptos and are using Blockchain technology to rewire the entire education system. For further details, visit quze.co<br>
                    In this workshop we will be discussing :
                </p>
