                        <img src="img/stavan2.jpeg" class="responsive-img" style="border-radius:50%">
                        <h4> Stavan Patel</h4>
                        <h5> Founder and CEO </h5>
                        <p>
                            Stavan is the CEO and Founder of Quze, which is a blockchain-based education platform that aims to connect learners, educators, employers and more. Stavan is a blockchain evangelist and wants to show people the value of this disruptive technology. He also shares a passion for teaching and has varied experience simplifying complex technological concepts to masses around the world. He has taught around Americas, Europe, Africa and Asia and understands how the education system can be evolved to fit the student of today. Before Quze, Stavan was working with Microsoft, developing custom-cloud solutions for Fortune-500 clients and creating intuitive user experiences
                        </p>

