                        <h4 style="margin-top:13px"> Jaya Lalwani</h4>
                        <h5> CFO </h5>
                        <p> Jaya is the business lead at Quze.
She found out about bitcoins and blockchains in the year 2015. Since then she has been a strong believer of the blockchain technology and is researching about the same.
She is a business management graduate specializing in risk management and investment banking. Being interested in how people make deep connections with each through learning - mostly online, she is now focused on helping create a learning platforms using future tech to rewire the learning ecosystem.
Before Quze, Jaya was working as a blockchain analyst to create blockchain based solutions for the banking sector in India and the Middle East.
                        </p>

